Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.10,0:01:55.76,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,100)\blur3}即刻绽放
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.17,0:02:00.43,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,100)\blur3}我定会前去迎你
